Invocation Name: rock paper scissors
des:
Have fun playing Rock, Paper, Scissors against Alexa!

Once you start the game, you can choose Rock, Paper, or Scissors. Alexa will also choose and let you know who wins. You can play for multiple rounds, and Alexa will keep track of your wins, losses, and ties. When you are done playing, just say stop to hear your results for the session.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
